                        <item xml:id="a1">
                           <locus target="#40r">f. 40r</locus>
                           <desc>: Donation note.</desc>
                           <quote xml:lang="gez">
                              <locus target="#40r">40r</locus>: ዘመጽሐፍ፡ ዘአቶ፡ ተክለ፡ ሃይማኖት፡ ዘአጽሐፎ፡ በንዋዩ፡
