                              ጴጥሮስ፡ ወጳውሎስ፡ ውጉዘ፡ ይኩን።</quote>
                           <quote xml:lang="en"/> Written in the main hand. The note mentions the
                           name of the commissioner and donor, ʾato<note> Takla Hāymānot. </note>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="e1">- Doodles: <locus target="#1r">1r</locus>, 1v, 23r,
